<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM3.10.8">
<l>allali liṉpa maḷaviṟan teṅku maḻakamar cūḻoḷiya</l>
<l>ṉalli malarmakaḷ pōka mayakkuka ḷākiyu niṟku mammā</l>
<l>ṉellaiyiṉ ñāṉattaṉ ñāṉa maḵtē koṇṭel lākkaru maṅkaḷuñce</l>
<l>yellaiyiṉ māyaṉaik kaṇṇaṉait tāḷpaṟṟi yāṉōrtuk kamilaṉē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The pervasive light that goes beyond the measure of painless pleasure, abiding in beauty everywhere,</l>
<l>the lord who stands, although being confusions, as the enjoyment of the woman from the lotus blossom,</l>
<l>the one who is boundless knowledge, the boundless trickster who takes that as knowledge</l>
<l>[and] does all deeds, holding on to Kṛṣṇa’s feet I am without any misery.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
